    "Id": "mechdef_dilletante_DLT-S2",
    "Name": "Dilletante",
    "Details": "The Dillettante is a new super heavy chassis from the Federated Commonwealth, continuing their love of autocannons, it mounts two rotary autocannons, both class 5, backed up by some Clan-spec ER PPCs and Large Pulse Lasers. The P2 variant replaces the rotary autocannon 2s of the P1 variant with a clan sourced Hyper-Gauss Rifle for improved armor penetration. Since all of its weapons have fairly long range, the designers were able to support such heavy firepower by putting a very small 270 XL engine, making the mech behave somewhat more like a mobile turret than a unit that can actually give chase. Nevertheless, the sheer amount of firepower on the mech allows it to perform as an excellent anvil for more mobile lance mates to drive enemies onto.<br><br>S-class mechs feature upgrades to their armour, thermal management and defensive systems that substantially improve their survivability on the 31st century battlefield.",
